'''奧斯汀·韋德·米多斯'''（{{lang-en|Austin Wade Meadows}}，{{bd|1995年|5月3日|}}），為[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]的[[外野手|外野手]]，目前效力於[[底特律老虎|底特律老虎]]。他先前曾效力過海盜與光芒等隊。

==職業生涯==
===匹茲堡海盜===
[[2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2013年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，海盜隊在第一輪第9順位選進米多斯。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/college/2013-top-100-draft-prospects-may-10-jonathan-gray-tops-mark-appel-for-top-sot/|title=2013 Top 100 Draft Prospects (May 10): Jonathan Gray Takes Top Spot - BaseballAmerica.com|date=May 10, 2013|publisher=|accessdate=April 18, 2017|archive-date=2017-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171214071407/https://www.baseballamerica.com/college/2013-top-100-draft-prospects-may-10-jonathan-gray-tops-mark-appel-for-top-sot/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://insider.espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/9255085/mark-appel-jonathan-gray-kris-bryant-top-prospects-2013-mlb-draft|title=Law: Top 100 draft prospects|publisher=|accessdate=April 18, 2017|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120259/http://insider.espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/9255085/mark-appel-jonathan-gray-kris-bryant-top-prospects-2013-mlb-draft|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在三週後與海盜簽下合約。<ref name=Sign>{{cite web|title=Pirates Agree to Terms with Austin Meadows|url=http://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2013/06/pirates-nearing-deal-with-austin-meadows.html|publisher=mlbtraderumors.com|date=June 27, 2013|accessdate=June 28, 2013|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710093814/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2013/06/pirates-nearing-deal-with-austin-meadows.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年開始，米多斯開啟他的職棒生涯。2014年，他因為繩肌拉傷而僅出賽38場比賽。2016年春訓，他因為右眼眼眶骨受傷而導致他出賽場次減少。<ref name=eye>{{cite web|url=http://www.altoonamirror.com/sports/local-sports/2016/03/meadows-injures-eye/|title=Meadows injures eye|work=Altoona Mirror|accessdate=April 18, 2017|archive-date=2017-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517231853/http://www.altoonamirror.com/sports/local-sports/2016/03/meadows-injures-eye/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年，球隊再次邀請他參加春訓，<ref name=vibe>{{cite web|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/sports/pirates/2017/03/19/Pirates-prospect-Austin-Meadows-major-league-spring-training/stories/201703190060|title=Pirates top prospect Austin Meadows getting major-league 'vibe'|publisher=|accessdate=April 18, 2017|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710060908/https://www.post-gazette.com/sports/pirates/2017/03/19/Pirates-prospect-Austin-Meadows-major-league-spring-training/stories/201703190060|dead-url=no}}</ref>並在球季結束後將他加入40人名單中。<ref>{{cite web |author=Rob Biertempfel |url=http://triblive.com/sports/pirates/12977361-74/pirates-put-austin-meadows-on-40-man-roster-gift-ngoepe-traded |title=Pirates put Austin Meadows on 40-man roster; Gift Ngoepe traded |publisher=TribLIVE |date=November 20, 2017 |accessdate=May 18, 2018 |archive-date=2018-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303013602/http://triblive.com/sports/pirates/12977361-74/pirates-put-austin-meadows-on-40-man-roster-gift-ngoepe-traded |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018年5月18日，米多斯升上大聯盟。他在初登場就敲出大聯盟首安和首盜。<ref>{{cite web |author=3:41 pm ET |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/23533618/pittsburgh-pirates-call-top-prospect-austin-meadows |title=Pittsburgh Pirates to call up top OF prospect Austin Meadows |publisher=Espn.com |date= |accessdate=May 18, 2018 |archive-date=2018-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180519121436/http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/23533618/pittsburgh-pirates-call-top-prospect-austin-meadows |dead-url=no }}</ref>5月20日，他敲出大聯盟首轟。<ref>{{cite web |author=3:35 pm ET |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/playbyplay?gameId=380520123 |title=San Diego Padres at Pittsburgh Pirates Boxscore |publisher=Espn.com |date= |accessdate=May 20, 2018 |archive-date=2020-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710094352/https://www.espn.com/mlb/playbyplay?gameId=380520123 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在5月繳出4成09打擊率，外帶7分打點與3次盜壘的成績，拿下國聯單月表現最佳新人獎。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://triblive.com/sports/pirates/13717106-74/austin-meadows-named-national-league-rookie-of-the-month |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-07-10 |archive-date=2018-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603213519/http://triblive.com/sports/pirates/13717106-74/austin-meadows-named-national-league-rookie-of-the-month |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===坦帕灣光芒===
2018年7月31日，海盜將米多斯、[[泰勒·格拉斯諾|泰勒·格拉斯諾]]還有一名日後指定球員（Shane Baz）交易至光芒，換來先發投手[[克理斯·亞契|克理斯·亞契]]，而米多斯也被下放到3A。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24246116/chris-archer-traded-pittsburgh-pirates-tampa-bay-rays |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-07-10 |archive-date=2018-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180804112121/http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24246116/chris-archer-traded-pittsburgh-pirates-tampa-bay-rays |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在9月19日達成光芒隊的初登場。他在光芒隊出賽10場比賽，打擊率為2成50，並敲出1轟與4分打點。<ref name="baseball-reference.com">{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/m/meadoau01.shtml|title=Austin Meadows Stats  {{!}} Baseball-Reference.com|website=Baseball-Reference.com|language=en|access-date=2018-10-02|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307190444/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/m/meadoau01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>合計整年他的打擊率為2成87，並敲出6轟與17分打點。

2019年，米多斯首度入選明星賽。<ref name="baseball-reference.com"/>該年他的打擊率2成91為全隊最高，外帶33轟與89分打點。

==個人生活==
米多斯從小就是亞特蘭大勇士的球迷。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ajc.com/sports/baseball/baseball-draft-goes-through-loganville/SBt4ij5i8F5yiiSY0vgkWO/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-07-10 |archive-date=2020-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710064007/https://www.ajc.com/sports/baseball/baseball-draft-goes-through-loganville/SBt4ij5i8F5yiiSY0vgkWO/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他的母親以前曾是喬治亞州立大學女壘隊的成員，而他父親曾在大學打過棒球和美式足球。他的弟弟Parker在2018年選秀會上被老虎隊在第二輪選走，目前仍在小聯盟打球。
